text: Cootje van Kampen-Tonneman (born 15 September 1921) was a Dutch gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hoorn
